OL,3,CHistoric mill destroyed in devastating
OL,4,Cfire
OL,6,FAerial footage shows the remains of
OL,7,Fone of Manchester's oldest buildings
OL,8,Fafter a devastating fire.
OL,10,FOne of Manchester's most recognisable
OL,11,Fand historic buildings has been
OL,12,Fdestroyed by a major fire.
OL,14,FThe derelict Hotspur Press building,
OL,15,Fbeside Oxford Road station in the city
OL,16,Fcentre, erupted into flames on Monday
OL,17,F23 June, with thick smoke clouds seen
OL,18,Ffor miles.
