OL,6,FThe major incident saw trains
OL,7,Fcancelled, main roads closed and more
OL,8,Fthan 180 residents evacuated from
OL,9,Fnearby high-rise buildings as
OL,10,Femergency services battled to bring
OL,11,Fthe flames under control.
OL,13,FAt the height of the fire, more than
OL,14,F20 fire engines, two aerial units and
OL,15,Fmore than 100 firefighters were
OL,16,Fworking at the scene, with some
OL,17,Fworking overnight to extinguish the
OL,18,Fblaze.
