OL,6,FDuring the incident, the fire spread
OL,7,Fto several balconies at the two tower
OL,8,Fblocks at number 1 Cambridge Street.
OL,10,FAll occupants made it out of the
OL,11,Fbuildings safely and there are "no
OL,12,Freports of any occupants suffering ill
OL,13,Fhealth", a Greater Manchester Fire and
OL,14,FRescue Service spokesperson said.
OL,16,FThey added: "Shortly after 9pm, the
OL,17,Fmajor incident was lifted.
