OL,6,F"The occupants of one of those blocks
OL,7,Fhave now been able to return home,
OL,8,Fwhile the other remains closed as we
OL,9,Fwork with Manchester City Council and
OL,10,Fthe building owner to make the
OL,11,Fbuilding habitable again.
OL,13,F"Oxford Road station and the railway
OL,14,Fline have now reopened. Crews are
OL,15,Fstill working on Gloucester Street and
OL,16,Fthe main area around the mill, but the
OL,17,Fmain roads of Whitworth and access off
OL,18,Fthe Mancunian Way have reopened."
