OL,6,F"Crews will be joined by specialist
OL,7,Ffire officers to begin investigating
OL,8,Fthe cause of the fire, as well as
OL,9,Fassessing the extent of the structural
OL,10,Fdamage to the building", they said.
OL,12,FThe Victorian building was originally
OL,13,Fbuilt as Medlock cotton mill in around
OL,14,F1801 and is considered Manchester's
OL,15,Foldest mill.
