OL,6,FIt was later repurposed as a printing
OL,7,Fworks by the Percy Brothers in the
OL,8,Flate 1800s, producing comics and
OL,9,Fjournals, but it failed to be
OL,10,Fredeveloped and modernised like its
OL,11,Fcounterparts.
OL,13,FIn recent years it had fallen into an
OL,14,Funinhabited derelict state.
OL,16,FIn May 2024, Manner, the company who
OL,17,Fhave owned the building since 2020,
OL,18,Fhad a planning application, to turn
OL,19,Fthe The Hotspur Press into a 37-storey
OL,20,Fblock of student flats, unanimously
OL,21,Fapproved by Manchester City Council.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
