OL,6,FThe plans were delayed due to changes
OL,7,Fin the design, but the company
OL,8,Fannounced in May 2025 that it was
OL,9,Fplanning to submit fresh proposals.
OL,11,FManner, who had vowed to "preserve the
OL,12,Ficonic Percy Brothers signage" and
OL,13,F"restore much of the existing brick
OL,14,Fexterior," has been approached by ITV
OL,15,FNews for comment.
OL,17,FA full investigation is underway to
OL,18,Festablish the cause of the fire.
